name: Setup CICD Environment
description: Update the SVT of Change Management module as per the environment selected in CICD Configuration wizard

arguments.env_type:
{% if vars.request.picklist | length == 2 %}{{vars.dev_prod}}{% elif
vars.request.picklist[0].itemValue == "Development" %}{{vars.dev}}{% else %}{{vars.prod}}{% endif %}

arguments.env_config: {% set env = [] %}{% for item in vars.request.picklist %}{% set _ = env.append({"itemValue": item. itemValue, "@id": item["@id"]}) %}{% endfor %}{{env}}

routes.name: Configuration -> Set CICD Config Global Variable
Create CICD Env Global Variable -> Get Env Type
